  <refsection id="Description_EVTDLY_f">
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>
One event is generated after an event enters the unique
input event port. The delay is defined by the dialogue 
parameter <emphasis role="bold">Delay</emphasis>.Block may also generate an initial
output event.   

</para>
  </refsection>
